<div type="original">
<pb f="1r" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1r-1" /><lb n="1" xml:id="l-1" />
<ab>Dimanche soir 5 Mai 89</ab>
<ns1:whiteline /><lb n="2" xml:id="l-2" />
<ab>Devant m’absenter demains et <lb n="3" xml:id="l-3" />étant occupé les Mardi, je me mets à <lb n="4" xml:id="l-4" />votre disposition pour vous accompagner <lb n="5" xml:id="l-5" />Mercredi à S<hi rend="ss">t</hi> Remy.<anchor n="1" xml:id="note-o-1" /> Nous partirions<hi rend="ital" /> <lb n="6" xml:id="l-6" />par le train de 8 heures 51, si cela vous <lb n="7" xml:id="l-7" />convient. Ayant déjà vu M. Peyron, il <lb n="8" xml:id="l-8" />est convenable que je vous accompagne <lb n="9" xml:id="l-9" />moi-même.<anchor n="2" xml:id="note-o-2" /></ab>
<ns1:whiteline /><lb n="9*" xml:id="l-9s" />
<ab>Bien à vous</ab><lb n="10" xml:id="l-10" />
<ab>Salles</ab>
<ns1:whiteline /></div>
<div type="translation">
<pb f="1r" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" />
<ab>Sunday evening, 5 May 1889</ab>
<ns1:whiteline />
<ab>Having to go away tomorrow and being busy on Tuesdays, I place myself at your disposal to accompany you to St-Rémy on Wednesday.<anchor n="1" xml:id="note-t-1" /> We would leave by the 8.51 train, if that suits you. Having already seen <rs key="568" type="pers">Mr Peyron</rs>, it is appropriate that I should accompany you myself.<anchor n="2" xml:id="note-t-2" /></ab>
<ns1:whiteline />
<ab>Yours truly,</ab>
<ab><rs key="663" type="pers">Salles</rs></ab>
<ns1:whiteline /></div>
<div type="notes">
<note n="1" target="#note-t-1" xml:id="n-1">
    <ab>Van Gogh and <rs key="663" type="pers">Salles</rs> left according to schedule on Wednesday, 8 May 1889 for the asylum of Saint-Paul-de-Mausole in Saint-Rémy. Van Gogh’s name was recorded on that date in <hi rend="ital">Le grand registre de l’asile de Saint-Rémy</hi>. <ref target="documentation.xml#id8May1889">See <hi rend="ital">Documentation</hi>, 8 May 1889</ref>. </ab></note>
    <note n="2" target="#note-t-2" xml:id="n-2">
<ab>On Monday, 29 April <rs key="663" type="pers">Salles</rs> had had a talk with <rs key="568" type="pers">Dr Peyron</rs> about Vincent’s admission to the asylum. <ref target="let763.xml">See letter 763</ref>, <hi rend="ital">Date</hi>.</ab></note></div></body></text></TEI>